For more information on Oz and Mozart see

	http://www.mozart-oz.org

We would appreciate if you could send E-mail to

	download@mozart-oz.org

with some brief information for what you plan to use Mozart.

Have lots of fun!

Fast track compilation for Ubuntu.
----------------------------------
$ sudo apt-get install tk-dev tcl-dev build-essential libc6-dev g++-multilib ia32-libs lib32z1-dev lib32gmp3-dev
$ mkdir ~/oz
$ mkdir -p ~/dev/mozart
$ cd ~/dev/mozart
$ git clone git://github.com/mozart/mozart.git
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ ../mozart/configure --prefix=/home/<username>/oz
$ make && make install

Fast track compilation for OS X
-------------------------------
install homebrew https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew + xcode dependency
$ brew install git emacs gmp gdbm zlib
$ mkdir ~/oz
$ mkdir -p ~/dev/mozart
$ cd ~/dev/mozart
$ git clone git://github.com/mozart/mozart.git
$ mkdir build 
$ cd build
$ ../mozart/configure --prefix=/Users/<username>/oz
$ make && make install

Installation.
-------------

Please refer to this website for more detail : http://www.mozart-oz.org/documentation/install/index.html
